    pol:hasContent "The Commission shall be empowered to review, by means of delegated acts in accordance with Article 23 of this Directive, the harmonised efficiency reference values laid down in Commission Implementing Decision 2011/877/EU on the basis of Directive 2004/8/EC by 31 December 2014." .

